A Beautiful Supercut of Alex Jones Making Bizarre Reptilian Growling Noises 
We sure this guy is human, though? Most Popular By Sammy Nickalls Feb 22, 2017 Alex Jones is a volcano, but instead of fiery lava, he lets out a lot of...noises. Sometimes, those noises come in the form of what non- InfoWars watchers would call " a conspiracy theory "; other times, it can only be defined as pure art . However, a recent viral mash-up of Jones's finest reptilian growls posted to Facebook by Super Deluxe may truly take the prize. Just watch him turn from right-wing conspiracy theorist to a straight-up lizard right before your very eyes:
